title: Buck Rogers 1939 Old Time Serial (OTS)
description:
This is an old time serial, a very early Buck Rogers serial composed of 12 episodes.  These were shown in theaters to get kiddies to come back every weekend to see the next episode and, incidentally, to pay for another admission.  They went on in the 40s to 60s and then faded out.  Later, cartoons went the same way.  Sad...

Synopsis:
A pilot and his young passenger crash-land on a mountaintop and are put into suspended animation by a strange gas. They awake 500 years later to discover that the Earth is now ruled by a tyrannical despot called Killer Kane, and they lead a fight to overthrow him
